author: Hannah Osborne
title: Coronavirus Outbreak May Have Started as Early as September, Scientists Say
description: The outbreak also may not have started in Wuhan, geneticist Peter Forster said.
content:
The coronavirus outbreak could have started as early as mid-September, and the Chinese city of Wuhan may not be where it began, a scientist looking at the origins of the disease has said.
